OL,3,CParliament to launch inquiry into
OL,4,CHorizon compensation delays
OL,6,FParliament is to launch an inquiry
OL,7,Flooking at delays in compensation
OL,8,Fsettlements for subpostmasters
OL,9,Fimpacted by the Horizon scandal, ITV
OL,10,FNews Reporter Chloe Keedy reports
OL,12,FWords by Senior Producer Isabel
OL,13,FAlderson-Blench
OL,15,FA parliamentary inquiry looking at
OL,16,Fdelays in compensation settlements for
OL,17,Fsubpostmasters impacted by the Horizon
OL,18,Fscandal will be launched next week.
