OL,3,CParliament to launch inquiry into
OL,4,CHorizon compensation delays
OL,6,FThe Business and Trade Select
OL,7,FCommittee will call government
OL,8,Fministers, subspostmasters and their
OL,9,Flawyers to give evidence across two
OL,10,Fsessions, starting in early November.
OL,12,FPost Office campaigner and chair of
OL,13,Fthe Justice for Subpostmasters
OL,14,FAlliance, Alan Bates, is expected to
OL,15,Fbe invited to give evidence.
OL,17,FThe inquiry will look into delays in
OL,18,Fsubpostmasters receiving full and
OL,19,Ffinal compensation, as well as the
OL,20,Fprocesses behind the different schemes.
