OL,3,CParliament to launch inquiry into
OL,4,CHorizon compensation delays
OL,6,FIn an exclusive interview with ITV
OL,7,FNews, chair of the Business & Trade
OL,8,FSelect Committee, Liam Byrne MP spoke
OL,9,Fon what is causing the delays.
OL,11,F"What ministers are tell us is there
OL,12,Fis definitely a delay in people coming
OL,13,Fforward and saying 'I suffered and I'm
OL,14,Fowed a redress payment'. Ministers
OL,15,Fwant people to step up and make sure
OL,16,Fthose applications are in," he said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
