OL,3,CParliament to launch inquiry into
OL,4,CHorizon compensation delays
OL,6,F"What we're hearing from
OL,7,Fsubpostmasters is that if there is an
OL,8,Fargument about how much should be paid
OL,9,Fout, the first offer is made quite
OL,10,Fquickly but if there's a negotiation,
OL,11,Fthat negotiation is dragging."
OL,13,FHe added that they want to hear from
OL,14,Fsubpostmasters to tell them what is
OL,15,F"still going wrong" and what ministers
OL,16,Fcan do to "speed it up."
