OL,3,CParliament to launch inquiry into
OL,4,CHorizon compensation delays
OL,6,FThe newly elected Business and Trade
OL,7,FCommittee met for the first time today
OL,8,Fto formally agree on the short inquiry
OL,9,Ftaking place. The first evidence
OL,10,Fsession is expected to take place at
OL,11,Fthe beginning of November, with the
OL,12,Fsecond session in mid-November.
OL,14,FMr Byrne said, "We on the committee
OL,15,Fare going to batter away at this, week
OL,16,Fin, week out, until it is job done.
OL,17,FAll of us on our committee are frankly
OL,18,Fhorrified and outraged by how long
OL,19,Fthis has taken and we're just not
OL,20,Fgoing to give up."
