OL,6,FFormer subpostmaster Joanne George is
OL,7,Fone of the 555 subpostmasters who were
OL,8,Fpart of the Group Litigation Order,
OL,9,Fwhich is administered by the
OL,10,FDepartment for Business and Trade. She
OL,11,Fhas not yet received her full
OL,12,Fcompensation settlement.
OL,14,FTen years ago, Jo and her husband Nick
OL,15,Fhad a home and three businesses - one
OL,16,Fof them a Post Office. Now, they are
OL,17,Fhomeless.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/17
