OL,6,FJo became the subpostmaster for
OL,7,FBaschurch Post Office in Shropshire in
OL,8,F2013, which she ran as a family
OL,9,Fbusiness alongside her husband, Nick,
OL,10,Fand son, Ross.
OL,12,FThey ran the Post Office for three
OL,13,Fyears, until an audit found a
OL,14,Fshortfall of #12,000 and Jo's contract
OL,15,Fwas terminated. She told us shortfalls
OL,16,Fwere constantly an issue.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/17
