OL,6,FFormer subpostmaster Joanne George
OL,7,Ftells ITV News she'd love her old life
OL,8,Fback 'before the Post office'
OL,10,F"There's many a time I've looked a
OL,11,Fcliff in Anglesey and thought, 'shall
OL,12,FI fly off that?'" Jo says.
OL,14,FOn the delay in compensation payments,
OL,15,Fshe says, "If they don't hurry up,
OL,16,Fwe'll all be dead. There's people
OL,17,Folder than us who have been fighting
OL,18,Flonger than us. If we're at the end of
OL,19,Four tether, I hate to think what
OL,20,Fthey're at the end of."
