OL,6,FA Post Office spokesperson said: "We
OL,7,Fapologise unreservedly for the hurt
OL,8,Fand suffering that was caused to
OL,9,Fvictims of the Horizon IT Scandal and
OL,10,Ftheir loved ones. Today's Post Office
OL,11,Fis focused on paying redress to those
OL,12,Faffected as quickly as possible so
OL,13,Fthey can move forward with their
OL,14,Flives."
