OL,6,FA spokesperson for the Department for
OL,7,FBusiness and Trade said: "We recognise
OL,8,Fthe immeasurable suffering postmasters
OL,9,Flike Joanne have endured and
OL,10,Funderstand their frustration after
OL,11,Fyears of inaction. But this Government
OL,12,Fis working tirelessly to provide full,
OL,13,Ffair and swift redress.
OL,15,F"At the end of September,
OL,16,Fapproximately #363 million has been
