OL,6,FThe group won their case against the
OL,7,FPost Office in December 2019, and the
OL,8,Fcourt awarded the 555 subpostmasters
OL,9,F#56.75m in damages. After legal costs,
OL,10,Fsubpostmasters were left with
OL,11,Fapproximately #21,000 each. Many
OL,12,Fsubpostmasters have criticised the
OL,13,Fdecision to make them cover their own
OL,14,Flegal fees.
