OL,3,CParliament to launch inquiry into
OL,4,CHorizon compensation delays
OL,6,FIn January 2024, the government
OL,7,Fannounced that it would be offering
OL,8,Fthe option of an increased immediate
OL,9,Fsettlement of #75,000 for each member
OL,10,Fof the GLO. Under this scheme,
OL,11,Fsubpostmasters can either accept
OL,12,F#75,000 upfront, or claim for more,
OL,13,Fdependent on their individual
OL,14,Fcircumstances.
OL,16,FAs of the end of September 2024, out
OL,17,Fof 555 GLO members, 208 had been paid
OL,18,Ffull and final compensation. This
OL,19,Fscheme is run by the Department for
OL,20,FBusiness and Trade
