OL,6,FThis scheme is for subpostmasters who
OL,7,Fwere not convicted of any crime, and
OL,8,Fwere not part of the Group Litigation
OL,9,FOrder, but who lost money as a result
OL,10,Fof Horizon issues.
OL,12,FIn March 2024 the government announced
OL,13,Fall eligible claimants to the Horizon
OL,14,FShortfall Scheme could settle for an
OL,15,Fimmediate #75,000 sum.
OL,17,FMore than 4,000 claims have been made
OL,18,Funder this scheme. Of these claims,
OL,19,F2,300 have been paid out. This scheme
OL,20,Fis run by the Post Office but claims
OL,21,Fare assessed by an independent panel.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/17
