OL,3,CParliament to launch inquiry into
OL,4,CHorizon compensation delays
OL,6,FThis scheme provides financial redress
OL,7,Fto those who were wrongfully convicted
OL,8,Fof Horizon-related offences. Following
OL,9,Fa law that was passed in May 2024,
OL,10,Fexonerating everyone who was convicted
OL,11,Fof Horizon-related offences between
OL,12,F1996 and 2018, hundreds more
OL,13,Fsubpostmasters are eligible for this
OL,14,Fscheme.
OL,16,FSubpostmasters can take an immediate
OL,17,F#600,000 upfront settlement, or can
OL,18,Fsubmit a full claim and enter into
OL,19,Fnegotiations if they believe they are
OL,20,Fentitled to more.
